  "comment": "onAir Flex Drive 2 is an LED Driver ideal for TV studios seeking simple and impactful on-camera looks with integrated power supply and driver for a one-box modular solution. onAir Flex Drive 2 features 24v to allow longer run lengths for set pieces and light boxes, and 8 channels of output for complete flexibility with a choice of tapes and lengths. It also features adjustable PWM, making it ideal for broadcast compatibility. With two outputs, onAir Flex Drive 2 supports RGBW or generic 4-channel control for up to 350W of total power and assisted convection cooling perfect for studio environments. To ease installation, onAir Flex Drive 2 also features DMX 5pin and Phoenix connector for installation support.",
